## 4. Pipeline Execution Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor App as Your App
    participant Engine as DexEngine
    participant Runner as PipelineRunner
    participant DuckDB as DuckDB
    participant Connectors as Connectors
    participant Transforms as Transforms
    participant Quality as Quality Gates
    participant Store as DexStore
    participant Catalog as DataCatalog

    App->>Engine: run_pipeline("etl")
    Engine->>Runner: run(name, progress_cb)
    Runner->>Connectors: read(source_config)
    Connectors->>DuckDB: DataFrame / Arrow Table
    Runner->>Transforms: execute DAG (filter, derive, cast...)
    Transforms->>DuckDB: Vectorised SQL per step
    Runner->>Quality: check(output, quality_config)
    Quality->>DuckDB: SELECT ... FROM _qc
    Quality-->>Runner: QualityResult
    Runner->>Store: record_lineage_event(...)
    Runner->>Store: record_pipeline_run(...)
    Runner->>Catalog: register_output_table(...)
    Runner-->>Engine: PipelineResult
    Engine-->>App: PipelineResult
```

