## 5. AI Agent + Tool Execution

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Engine as DexEngine
    participant Agent as Agent Runtime
    participant Router as ModelRouter
    participant Privacy as PrivacyGuard
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant Tools as Tool Registry
    participant Memory as AI Memory
    participant Store as DexStore

    User->>Engine: agents["analyst"].chat("top 5 customers")
    Engine->>Agent: run(task)
    Agent->>Router: route(messages, tools)
    Router->>Privacy: mask_pii(prompt)
    Privacy->>LLM: call(masked_prompt, tools)
    LLM-->>Privacy: tool_calls / text
    Privacy-->>Router: unmask(response)
    Router->>Agent: tool_calls
    par Tool Execution
        Agent->>Tools: call("query", sql="...")
        Tools->>Store: execute SQL via DuckDB
        Store-->>Tools: result rows
        Tools-->>Agent: tool_result
    end
    Agent->>Memory: store_episode(task, steps, outcome)
    Memory->>Store: INSERT INTO ai_episodes
    Agent-->>Engine: AgentResult(text, citations)
    Engine-->>User: Response
```

